      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "### Release Notes\r\n\r\n#### New Features\r\n\r\n1. Base File Integration: Clicking on Zen Space now automatically creates and opens a base file within the selected folder\r\n\r\n#### Improvements\r\n\r\n1. Index files are now named after their parent folder (e.g., FolderName.md instead of Index.md)\r\n2. Updated to use the new cssclasses property instead of the deprecated cssclass\r\n3. Improved CSS class formatting to properly handle arrays/lists\r\n\r\n#### Bug Fixes\r\n\r\n1. Fixed navigation history management for back and forward buttons\r\n2. Improved file filtering and display logic in the Zen Space view\r\n3. Enhanced error handling for file operations\r\n4. File operations in the native file explorer are properly reflected in index files",
